snippet.title: Tatara Kogasa's Surprise Operation (v1.1.1 / Post-Jam version) - Gameplay demonstration
snippet.description:
Touhou jam game i worked on last month with two other people. I composed the ost for it!

Download the game here: https://lever210.itch.io/tatara-kogasas-surprise-operation
Listen to the OST in my second channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D44x8J704y8&list=PLSFkTrqmoH7tuyc6G3O-4x7_wMa1Jq204
